  "vulnerability_information": "Apache was vulnerable to a pause-based desync. This vulnerability is described in detail in my whitepaper here: https://portswigger.net/research/browser-powered-desync-attacks#pause\n\n## Impact\n\nThis enables server-side HTTP Request Smuggling when Apache is deployed as a back-end server, and it also enables MITM attackers to inject arbitrary JavaScript in spite of TLS.",
